{
  "texts": [
    "However, when such tools are used, it is essential that the responses given are relevant and accurate.",
    "Thus, assessing the LLM's capacity to accurately answer and explain the community medicine examination questions and concepts administered to students is imperative.",
    "Furthermore, such evaluations will provide a better understanding of how language models can be used in medical education and the challenges that must be overcome to fully realize their potential.",
    "In this background, the primary aim of this study was to validate the ability of ChatGPT to answer the undergraduate medical community medicine examination.",
    "We also compared the scores obtained on the examination by ChatGPT with those obtained by the students."
  ]
}